OL,3,CPublic inquiry to be held into police
OL,4,Cfailings in Emma Caldwell murder
OL,6,FMs Caldwell was killed by serial
OL,7,Frapist Iain Packer in 2005 - but while
OL,8,Fofficers interviewed him a month after
OL,9,Fher body was found in May that year,
OL,10,Fhe was convicted of her murder, along
OL,11,Fwith a series of rapes and other
OL,12,Foffences just last week.
OL,14,FPolice Scotland has already apologised
OL,15,Fto the family of Ms Caldwell and his
OL,16,Fother victims, saying they were "let
OL,17,Fdown" by policing in 2005.
