OL,3,CPublic inquiry to be held into police
OL,4,Cfailings in Emma Caldwell murder
OL,6,FThe announcement comes after both
OL,7,FScottish First Minister Humza Yousaf
OL,8,Fand his Justice Secretary Angela
OL,9,FConstance met with the murdered
OL,10,Fwoman's mother earlier this week.
OL,12,FMs Constance told MSPs that Ms
OL,13,FCaldwell's mother told her: "My
OL,14,Fdaughter Emma and the many victims who
OL,15,Fso courageously spoke up deserve
OL,16,Fnothing less than a robust,
OL,17,Findependent public inquiry and a judge
OL,18,Fwho will act without fear or favour.
