OL,4,Cfailings in Emma Caldwell murder
OL,6,F"There are those who say that such
OL,7,Finquiries take too long. My family
OL,8,Fhave struggled for 19 years to get
OL,9,Fjustice and we will wait however long
OL,10,Fit takes to see the truth, and will
OL,11,Faccept nothing less."
OL,13,FWith Packer planning to appeal both
OL,14,Fhis convictions and sentence, Ms
OL,15,FConstance stressed there are
OL,16,F"restrictions" on what she can say
OL,17,Fabout the case.
OL,19,FLast week Packer was jailed for Ms
OL,20,FCaldwell's murder and will serve a
OL,21,Fminimum 36 years.
