OL,3,CPublic inquiry to be held into police
OL,4,Cfailings in Emma Caldwell murder
OL,6,FDuring the court hearings, lawyers
OL,7,Frepresenting Ms Caldwell's family said
OL,8,Fit was one of Police Scotland's most
OL,9,Fexpensive and complex investigations
OL,10,Fever.
OL,12,FThey claim #4 million was spent on
OL,13,Fwrongly accusing four Turkish men, who
OL,14,Fappeared in court in 2007, who were
OL,15,Flater found innocent.
OL,17,Fin 2005, Ms Caldwell vanished days
OL,18,Fafter telling her mother Margaret
OL,19,Fabout her hopes to overcome a heroin
OL,20,Faddiction, which she funded with sex
OL,21,Fwork in Glasgow.
