OL,3,CPublic inquiry to be held into police
OL,4,Cfailings in Emma Caldwell murder
OL,6,FShe came from a close-knit family -
OL,7,Fher struggles with drugs began
OL,8,Ffollowing the death of her sister in
OL,9,Fher early 20s.
OL,11,FShe saw both parents twice a week and
OL,12,Fspoke to them daily.
OL,14,FHer family reported her missing after
OL,15,Fshe failed to respond to attempts by
OL,16,Fthem to change a planned meeting.
OL,18,FA dog walker found Ms Caldwell's body
OL,19,Fin woodland, with a "garotte" around
OL,20,Fher neck, a month after her
OL,21,Fdisappearance.
